 * If you want to utilize the Yahoo mapping feature, you must request an API key for your site
 * here: http://api.search.yahoo.com/webservices/register_application
 *
 * Enter your API key below to enable the mapping feature for your CiviCRM installation.
 * 
 * For Yahoo for yahoo Maps and Google for google maps 	
 * 
 */
